Repository - collection of works on samsung innovation campus internet things 2025-2026. 
Stack: C++; platform.io; esp32 (similar to arduino).

1. Project_Room_Lux - There is a room with a door that is locked with an electronic lock. 
    This lock is opened by entering a code on a four-button keypad.
    The device must have a visual indicator. When the door is closed, the LED is on.
    After pressing the buttons in the correct order, the door opens and remains open for 10 seconds,
    during which the LED flashes. After that, the door closes and the LED turns on continuously again.
    The door only closes at night.

